{"tid":659840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵招標二維碼 QR Code 收費系統","createTime":"2018-05-10T07:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T09:01:36.000Z","uid":98982,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"29ae9ee70eeea1dc5d621b5aa7729c983eb036f0","tid":659840,"uid":98982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T07:56:14.000Z","msg":"電子付費技術日漸成熟，各地的服務供應商亦相繼攻港，坊間亦有不少期望港鐵早日支援 Apple Pay 等手機支付服務的聲音。然而，從港鐵近日公開的招標公告可見，<span style=\"color: red;\">二維碼（QR Code）將有望成為港鐵最優先考慮的電子付費方案，而採用近場通訊（NFC）技術的方式，恐怕不容樂觀。</span><br />\n<br />\n事實上，港鐵早於機場快綫採用 QR Code 充當車票，讓乘客入閘，但尚未正式用於收費系統。然而，與現行的八達通卡技術相比，用家需要先打開應用程式，掃瞄 QR Code ，再等待授權才能夠成功入閘。在本身已十分繁忙的港鐵站使用，更有可能加劇車站的擠迫情況。<br />\n<br />\n其實，北京、上海及日本等地早已支援 iOS 的錢包功能，讓用家可將交通卡加進應用程式之中，以免驗證方式付費入閘。對每日人流龐大的港鐵而言，使用 QR Code 到底是進步還是倒退，就要留待官方公布更多消息。港鐵招標公告如下：<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/2-8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F2-8.png&h=cf664ce3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52c6e8b284bb9e0c89be3ccd0893b9176bcd19c3","tid":659840,"uid":98982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T07:57:47.000Z","msg":"可以排5分鐘隊入閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ba6c27ff34174f989580bdff73667c49f67971","tid":659840,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52c6e8b284bb9e0c89be3ccd0893b9176bcd19c3","tid":659840,"uid":98982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T07:57:47.000Z","msg":"可以排5分鐘隊入閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T07:59:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16263e459a021ed8a74091c35212fbdb0b40d7c","tid":659840,"uid":76349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:12:21.000Z","msg":"個套路就咁既：招標價低者得，跟住支拿公司中標，再來做到一pat屎/爛尾，之後就追加撥款咁，最後又係係我地個荷包度搶錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a5908bbed9b27cc29598ee4a0409dd2f06c712","tid":659840,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2ba6c27ff34174f989580bdff73667c49f67971","tid":659840,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52c6e8b284bb9e0c89be3ccd0893b9176bcd19c3","tid":659840,"uid":98982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T07:57:47.000Z","msg":"可以排5分鐘隊入閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T07:59:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:14:12.000Z","msg":"香港站機鐵已用QR Code 入閘，但佢scan果個位好光，電話反光Mon貼會搞到嘟唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7144078d4fe03696cd849bd938a843a0f46a2fca","tid":659840,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7a5908bbed9b27cc29598ee4a0409dd2f06c712","tid":659840,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2ba6c27ff34174f989580bdff73667c49f67971","tid":659840,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52c6e8b284bb9e0c89be3ccd0893b9176bcd19c3","tid":659840,"uid":98982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T07:57:47.000Z","msg":"可以排5分鐘隊入閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T07:59:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:14:12.000Z","msg":"香港站機鐵已用QR Code 入閘，但佢scan果個位好光，電話反光Mon貼會搞到嘟唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:54:17.000Z","msg":"試驗過 咁多問題<br />\n仲繼續玩落去<br />\n真係馬鹿野郎"},{"pid":"1041297d32d14b1b44976d24960d95b8dae3b3ab","tid":659840,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T09:00:29.000Z","msg":"支那寶微信支付中硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"